<div class="home">
  <div class="top">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>We are building Ampercoin, a digital currency like Bitcoin.</h2>
      <p>Here's what makes it different:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Ampercoins are worth $1 USD</li>
        <li>Easy to remember addresses</li>
        <li>Minimal energy consumption</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="preorder container">
    <h1>Preorder your Ampercoin address today</h1>
    <div class='checkout'>
<form accept-charset="UTF-8" action="/addresses" class="inline" id="new_address" method="post">
  <div class="form-group form-group-lg">
    <div class="col-sm-offset-3 col-md-5">
      <div class="input-group">
        <div class="input-group-addon">&</div>
        {{input type="text" class="form-control" id="address" name="address" value=address placeholder="bob"}}
      </div>
    </div>
    <button type="submit" class="checkout" type="submit" {{action 'createOrder'}} />
      <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i>
    </button>
  </div>
  </form>
    <div class="col-md-offset-3 col-md-6 text-center">
      *All Ampercoin accounts will come with 10 Ampercoins.
    </div>
  <div class="about container">
      <a name="about" id="about"></a>
      <section>
        <h1>Details</h1>
        <article>
          <h2><i class="fa fa-certificate"></i>Stablity</h2>
          <p>The value of Ampercoin will be pegged to the value of the US Dollar. Ampercoin farmers will track exchange rates. If the value is too high, farmers will create more currency. If the value is too low they will destroy it.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2><i class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up"></i>&you</h2>
          <p>Ampercoin addresses are shorter and much easier to remember then bitcoin addresses. Just like you have the twitter handle @mason you could have an Ampercoin address &amp;mason.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2><i class="fa fa-leaf"></i>Green</h2>
          <p>Bitcoin is burning $15 million dollars worth of energy every day. Ampercoin is based on a different algorithm which will take very little energy to run.</p>
        </article>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h1>Technical Details</h1>
        <article>
          <h2><i class="fa fa-code"></i>Modern Stack</h2>
          <p>The Ampercoin reference client is written in Ruby on Rails. Ampercoin aims to be as simple as possible. Smart contracts/messaging/asset exchanges are all better suited for <a href="http://www.nxtcommunity.org/">NXT Coin</a>.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2><i class="fa fa-warning"></i>Under Construction</h2>
          <p>The <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/masonforest/ampercoin-node">Ampercoin node</a> and a <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/masonforest/ampercoin-cli">command line client</a> are under development. Please contribute if you are a developer. If you are interested in Ampercoin please help fund the project by preordering Ampercoins.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2><i class="fa fa-tree"></i>Proof of Plant</h2>
          <p>Blocks are mined via a new algorithm called "Proof of Plant". Ampercoins are planted and can be harvested for more Ampercoins at a later date.</p>
        </article>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
